parameters: I can enter the building from here.
You two. You want to meet Lord Kann, right?
Then let me help you out♥
Why do you know of our...
I've been watching you all this time, you know.
Do you think I'd let a male out of my sight?
You see, this one's... a woman!
No wonder she has such a cute face...
That's why she can't be your prey.
Even if you're dressed as a civilized lady,
I'm not going to charm you right here, y'know?
Is there a way to meet miss Kannryuua?
To be more precise, we can give you that opportunity.
You an acquaintance of hers or something?
In the first place, even if you come across
her, it can be real hard to get a word in──
──Let's skip to the main part then.
Participate in the Hersteide Festival and win.
Then, you'll be invited to the Glory of Hersteide.
The Hersteide Festival is a tournament of power.
Braggarts fight to claim the title of strongest.
S-so it's that kind of tournament?
I thought it'd be more fun than that.
Everyone enjoys the spectacle, you know?
Back in the day, strength is everything in Torion.
You didn't approach me just to lecture
me about miss Kannryuua and the tournament, right?
In the first place, you can't join the tournament by
just being here. There's a bunch of requirements
If you listen to my request, I'll tell you all about
those conditions── No, I'll help you satisfy
all of the conditions to enter!
A Succubus's request ain't no joke.
If it comes down to it, I'll leave it to you.
No, you can't just ditch that on me!
We'll hear your request. Be assured,
we'll complete it in due haste.
I expected you to say that.
Please come with me to a certain place.
A certain place? Be more specific, dammit.
And you have more than one request?
Take me in as one of your companions.
I want to meet Lord Kann, too.
So, let me fight alongside you.
It's already dangerous enough to walk around
with a Succubus, and now you're letting her
Fiede's here with me, after all.
Let's do our best together, okay?♥
At the shop where I work.
It's at the end of Succubus Street...
though I wonder if it's a good idea to just
pass through Succubus Street as is...
It should be connected to north entrance right
Out from Decadent Street is the west
Would you kindly tell me your name?
Ah, so you do know my name...
